  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为医疗管理系统设计一个FastAPI应用架构。核心模块包括患者、服务提供方、医疗服务这几个实体，它们需要跟预约和理赔模块交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Patient Module",
        "Provider Module",
        "Service Module",
        "Appointment Module",
        "Claim Module"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，这几个都是核心业务实体。那理赔之后是不是还需要支付模块？另外审计方面怎么处理？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Claim Module",
        "Payment Module",
        "Audit Module with Bedrock AI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，理赔模块要驱动支付，而且支付和理赔都需要被审计。我们这次想引入Bedrock AI做智能审计分析，所以审计模块要单独标注出来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Claim Module",
        "Payment Module",
        "Audit Module with Bedrock AI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那我把所有模块都放在FastAPI Application的子图里。患者、服务提供方、医疗服务这三个作为基础实体，统一用绿色系；预约、理赔、支付作为业务流程，用蓝色系；审计模块带AI能力，用橙色系突出，您看这样区分合理吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Patient Module",
        "Provider Module",
        "Service Module",
        "Appointment Module",
        "Claim Module",
        "Payment Module",
        "Audit Module with Bedrock AI",
        "subgraph"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "颜色区分很清晰。不过确认一下，患者、服务提供方、医疗服务这三个模块，它们跟预约和理赔的关系是怎样的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Patient Module",
        "Provider Module",
        "Service Module",
        "Appointment Module",
        "Claim Module"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "我理解的是这三个基础实体都会参与预约创建，也都会产生理赔数据。所以是P、PR、S都指向A，同时也都指向C，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Patient Module",
        "Provider Module",
        "Service Module",
        "Appointment Module",
        "Claim Module"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，就是这样。然后理赔模块要触发支付，同时理赔和支付都要被审计模块记录。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Claim Module",
        "Payment Module",
        "Audit Module with Bedrock AI"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我现在把结构画出来。七个模块都在FastAPI Application子图内，关系线按您说的连接：三个基础实体连到预约和理赔，理赔连到支付和审计，支付也连到审计。",
      "elements_involved": [
